{"tid":1660574,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[熟勞工法入］冇簽約 做唔夠一個月 要賠錢先走得?","createTime":"2019-10-17T14:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T10:24:01.000Z","uid":275640,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f7322fd488dfca9c41726d9b5fd04f9333ec49cc","tid":1660574,"uid":275640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"背景： <br />\n<br />\n［member]搵到份工 (ft sales)<br />\n每個月 出現金 有糧單<br />\n每日返工放工 要簽紙 同電腦打卡<br />\n我有save低證據 證明我返過工<br />\n<br />\n間野賣淘寶野扮上菜 <br />\n佢有～10間分店<br />\n<br />\n做左廿日都冇 <br />\n我覺得唔適合就同老細講辭職<br />\n佢唔係香港 所以wts 度話接受我辭職<br />\n但叫我賠返十日代通知金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為編左更表比我WO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入職時我無簽過合約<br />\n一開頭 wts 講兩個月probation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（有白紙黑字證明<br />\n依家 閪老細搬龍門死拗 <br />\n轉口話無試用期<br />\n死都要我賠錢<br />\n出十幾日糧 意圖扣十日糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入職 在職期間<br />\n閪老細從未提過離職安排 <br />\n我離左職 突然先講 辭職要通知期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢走法律漏洞定點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲話同左勞工處講 要求介入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求熟勞工法巴絲 比一比意見<br />\n我第一次遇到咁撚閪既老細<br />\n野蠻到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：第一次 返出現金又冇合約既工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/member]"},{"pid":"4ed2a033aa17961346326568ca3305ee891c7de0","tid":1660574,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04Z2Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04Z2Gp.jpg&h=e79a1d2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ae1cddcbf3a1dbca21d6c994502bfff0d604c9b5","tid":1660574,"uid":275640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7322fd488dfca9c417